videos.headline: Vedral connects with Melton for a 29-yard Rutgers TD
videos.description: Noah Vedral floats a pass to Bo Melton to give the Scarlet Knights an early lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Vedral connects with Melton for a 29-yard Rutgers TD) 2020/11/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Rutgers cashes in on Melton's great TD catch-and-run
videos.description: Noah Vedral throws over the middle to Bo Melton, who makes the grab and takes it to the house for a 66-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Rutgers cashes in on Melton’s great TD catch-and-run) 2020/11/14 ESHEET
